column5: Just curious. My frugal side is showin, I know I will end up paying the $11 for parking, and $32 to get in, but I am trying here
Limited free parking at Ontario Place will save you $11 and an OFAH membership will save you another $2. How's that for a start?
There are $2.00 off coupons in the Toronto Sun Sportsman Show Pull-Out if anyone is looking. Todays paper
